0.Instruction: Bring your right arm across the table, horizontally, towards your left shoulder.

1.Instruction: Then extend your right arm back out as far as you can towards your right side.

2.Instruction: Place a pink post-it anywhere on the left side of the table.

3.Instruction: Place a yellow sticky post-it pad above the pink one in a column.

4.Instruction: Place a blue sticky post-it pad above the yellow one in a column.

5.Instruction: Place a green cube as far as you can on your right side, opposite to the pink post-it note.

6.Instruction: Place an orange cube right above the green cube.

7.Instruction: Place a blue cube above the orange cube.

8.Instruction: Move the green cube to the pink post-it note.

9.Instruction: Move the blue cube to the blue post-it note.

10.Instruction: Move the orange cube to the yellow post-it note.
